    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead-big">Zoom is an effective communication tools that allow us to all stay connected from home.</span></p>
<p>However, as it has the functionality to collect personal information via recordings, accounts used to set them up, chats and sharing of documents, it is important to highlight a few key data protection considerations.</p>]]></Value>
